Dartmouth was especially weak in goal kicking as of all her five trials, which were right in front of the goal, she only secured two goals.

abstract: WILLIAMSTOWN, Mass., Nov. 12. -- The defeat of the football team by Dartmouth last Saturday has not left the college utterly hopeless.
